name: 1980 200 Mints Commemorative Insert - #TZ200
description:
On December 27th, 2021, thr33som3s minted his 200th mint on the Tezos blockchain.  Each one was minted on the hic et nunc contract on H=N or a mirror site. 

This Insert commemorates those 200 mints. It was originally made available for free via airdrop to every verified member of The Grotto at the time it was minted.  It is a special token of thanks for all the interest and engagement and support The Grotto has provided me this year.

The first 200 Tezos mints produced 81,757 total editions. At the time of this writing, 37,416 of those editions have been burned for Utility.  Those of you who receive this token will have to figure out its Utility and decide for yourselves what to do with it.
